==================
Gnome Specimen 0.4
==================

User-visible changes since the previous release:
- Added a preview label so that fonts are immediately shown (lp:#175894)
- Adding font family only adds first variant/style (lp:#124274)
- Added tooltips to some widgets (lp:#119202)
- Select parent row after collapsing font family (lp:#175893)
- Improved treeview scrolling code a bit

Other changes:
- Added 22x22 application icon
- Updated .desktop file

Translations:
- Arabic (Khaled Hosny)
- Dutch (Wouter Bolsterlee)


